Manifest of files needed for the Ryan and Robbie site
with a short description of their purpose

Top Level HTML files
 
 index.html       .... main page
 authors.html     .... authors (about) page
 shop.html        .... shop (buy the book!) page

 randrfinal.css   .... the file for my css 

 randrfinal.html  .... old file for trying things out
                       (somewhat broken at this point)
 README           .... README for Github

 favicon.ico      .... my attempt at a favicon. Not definitive. 
                       I was trying to take the R&R from the logo
                       and make it recognizable at favicon sizes. 
                       Not entirely successful

 slide1.html      .... HTML versions of the slides 
 slide2.html        (to be used to regenerate the slideshow images
 slide3.html          if one wants to change the content 
 slide4.html             or the font. Take screenshots. )

